thread.title: Shawn Gagne

author: Shawn Gagne
title: Shawn Gagne
text: This is the second time where I have placed an order and had pieces missing. The first time was when I purchased a valve cover gasket, it had been opened and one of the spark plug gaskets was missing. Now I have this order, parts of the kit are missing, and half of the tool I rented is missing. Someone needs to check these orders better before they are shipped. Edit- Spoke with them on the phone and they made it right with no hassle, good customer service.
